---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Uncle Crumbles — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Bakery on Main, rebranding to Uncle Crumbles after 30 years, cut its catalog from 40 SKUs to under 10, raised its food-safety score from 87 to 99, and added a Formic palletizer to end 50-pound hand-stacking."
  ogTitle="Uncle Crumbles — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="SQF 87 → 99 · 40 → <10 SKUs · no more 50-lb hand-stacking"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/uncle-crumbles" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Uncle Crumbles
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Uncle Crumbles</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">How Automation Is Powering the Next Chapter at Uncle Crumbles</h1>
    <p class="lede">Bakery on Main — rebranding to Uncle Crumbles after 30 years — cut its catalog from 40 SKUs to under 10, raised its food-safety score from 87 to 99, and added a Formic palletizer so its people no longer hand-stack 50-pound boxes.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/uncle-crumbles-hero.jpg" alt="Uncle Crumbles granola production" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Uncle Crumbles · Connecticut</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">In business</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">~30 years</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Connecticut</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Granola, oats, oatmeal</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Standard</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">All-natural / gluten-free</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Schedule</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">24 hrs/day · 5 days/wk</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Reinventing a <em>30-year-old company</em>.</h2>
      <p>Bakery on Main, a 30-year-old Connecticut company rebranding to Uncle Crumbles, makes granola and oats and is expanding into oatmeal. CEO James Shutts, who joined about two years ago, cut the catalog from 40 SKUs to fewer than 10 and raised the Safe Quality Food score from 87 to 99 — and is now bidding on top-5 grocer business the company previously couldn't even answer.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Catalog cut from 40 SKUs to fewer than 10</li>
        <li>Safe Quality Food score raised from 87 to 99</li>
        <li>Now bidding on top-5 grocer business</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/uncle-crumbles-2.jpg" alt="Uncle Crumbles granola and oats packaging" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Granola · oats · oatmeal</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic robotic palletizer" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">$0 CapEx · monthly</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Stop hand-stacking <em>50-pound boxes</em>.</h2>
      <p>After a prior "robot graveyard" of failed used equipment, the company partnered with Formic for palletizing. The Formic palletizer — going live within weeks — solves manual stacking of 50-pound boxes, with fast deployment, monthly contracts, $0 CapEx, and full preventative and corrective maintenance. The plant runs 24 hours a day, five days a week, and the plan is to retrain and upskill current employees.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Solves manual 50-pound box stacking</li>
        <li>Fast deployment, monthly contract, $0 CapEx</li>
        <li>Retrain and upskill current staff</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"We literally hand palletize 50-pound boxes. I can't ask my employees to do that."</blockquote>
      <cite>James Shutts · CEO, Uncle Crumbles</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">The reins <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">are free now.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">99</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">SQF score (up from 87)</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">&lt;10</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">SKUs (down from 40)</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">$0</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">CapEx</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Power your <em>next chapter</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
